【About IRICO】









 





 


 
【Headquarters of IRICO Group Corp. in Beijing】

【Production Base in Xi’an & Xianyang】
 
【Production Base in Yangtze River Delta】
 

 
【Production Base in Extensive Yangtze River Delta】
 
 
 
【Production Base in Pearl River Delta】 
        IRICO Group Corporation (namely “IRICO Group”) is the central enterprise under the SASAC of the State Council. The headquarters of IRICO Group is at No.11 Xinxi Road, Shangdi, Haidian District. The main production base is in Xi’an-xianyang, Yangtz River, Extensive Yangtz River and Pear River Deltas. The main business is oriented to “the R&D and manufacture of the display device and its components, optoelectronic complete set and related components”. Up to the first half year of 2010, IRICO Group had realized total sales revenue of more than 100 billion RMB yuan and profit tax by over 10 billion RMB yuan. It contributed excellently to the China’s electronic information industry.
        IRICO Group Corporation was formerly named Shaanxi IRICO Color Picture Tube Plant (Coded 4400) and was established in the 1970s. It was a state-owned sole proprietorship enterprise established under the concert and approval of the leaders of Central CPC Committee and the State Council for the China’s color TVs industry. After the development and grandness of over 30 years, IRICO Group has already grown up to the influential group in electronic information enterprise. It has 13 second level solely funded and holding sub-companies and 8 joint stock companies; it also has two listed companies: IRICO Stock (600707.SH) and IRICO Electronics (0438.HK).  The company now has total assets of near 10 billion RMB yuan and near 20,000 employees.
        For over the past three decades, after overcoming countless of difficulties and frustrations, IRICO people has always been holding the strong willpower and industriously perfecting its business, they based upon the domestic market and gestated many No.1 in the electronic information industry in China. IRICO is the birthplace of the first CPT and the first set of CPT glass bulb in China; it is a CPT production company with the greatest production capacity and most powerful assorting capacity in China, which has also sent a colorful world for over 100 million of families in total. IRICO is the birthplace of the first projection tube in China, its self-developed projection tube with big screen, high brightness and high definition once ranked the famous branded product in the same business in the world. IRICO is the birthplace of the first piece of PDP display device in China; it’s the unique PDP middle testing line in China once made tremendous contribution to the development of the new display devices in China. IRICO is the birthplace of the first piece of OLED display device in China, since its starting investment and attempts in 1997, it has made the breakthrough for the development of OLED business in China, IRICO is also the birthplace of the first TFT-LCD glass substrate in China, its self-owned intellectual property in glass substrate added up the vancancy in China, smashed the technical blockade from the foreign countries for many years and rewrote the history of the disability for China to produce TFT-LCD glass substrate. IRICO will soon make the new breakthrough in above Gen.8 LCD glass substrate and the Gen.3 TV-use display devices ---AM-OLED, which shall make new contributions to the display devices industry in China.  
        IRICO Group has been sticking the development trace characterized by “Make the Corporate More Stronger with the Help of Technology” while it constantly upgrades the business scale and managerial level. She, stood besides the profound cultural accumulation and resource advantages, has already established the enterprise technical centre of state-level, patent workstation and post doctor workstation, moreover, the company has been honored with many rewards like the National Scientific & Technological Advance Prize, Top-100 leading informationized enterprises in China, it has been awarded with the honorary titles of “National Innovative Enterprise”, “National Enterprises and Government Units Intellectual Property Demonstration Company”. Currently, the business of CPT, LCD Glass and Illumination Materials, etc. in IRICO occupies the leading position in the world, and the business of green lighting, LED chips, OLED, PV glass, etc. ranks the leading position in the domestic market.
        For many years, the Party Central Committee and the State Council have always been concerning and supporting the development of IRICO. The leaders of the CPC and the country visited the IRICO to inspect and direct the work successively, such as Hu Jintao, Jiang Zemin, Wu Bangguo, Wen Jiabao and Zhang Dejiang, etc. they also gave the fully recognition and highly appraisal for the development of IRICO.  
        Since the negative affects brought by the shock of the financial crisis and the upgrading of the industry in the past couple of years, under the leadership of the general manager ,Xing Daoqin and the leading group, all the IRICO people have been insisting the guidance of scientific development outlook, jointing everyone’s hands to work together to conquer the current difficulties with strong willpower and sparing no efforts to propel the strategic transformation of the company, the company has successfully accomplished the new stride from “To make the CPTs Stronger and Innovate the business” to “Make Restructuring to Optimization, Strive for Strongness in a Steady and Quick Way”, which has been coming into form of the strategic pattern featured by the three major business clusters, IRICO Group Corp. and its listing subsidiaries——IRICO Display Devices Co. Ltd. and IRICO Group Electronics Co. Ltd., which lay special emphasis on developing the photoelectron related business(specifically develops the LED Epi-wafer & chip, LED encapsulation, LED illumination, LED display panel, LED backlight and new energy resources, etc.), display devices business(specially develops the newly display devices like LCD, OLED, PDP, FED, etc. and CPT) and components materials business (specially develops electronic glass products, illumination materials and metal components, etc.), respectively. The company has basically accomplished the development transformation from the simplification in business to that in diversification, some further enhancement has been made in the aspects of company vitality, controlling force and influence.
         Looking forward to the future, IRICO people has full confidence and enthusiasm; they are ready to abide the managerial concept of “Creator of the Happy life for Mankind.”, and strictly conform to the corporate spirit of “For People, For Business; In Pursuit of Excellent”, the company shall be based upon the chief business positioning and determine to make the IRICO Group Corp. to be the most fast growing company in the photoelectron field of the electronic information industry in China. IRICO is fully prepared to make much more contributions to accomplishing the targets of the construction of an innovative nation and a harmonious society.

 







 














