irico group new energy compa (438) Details


			IRICO Group New Energy Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in solar photovoltaic, new materials, trading, and other businesses in the People’s Republic of China, Hong Kong, and internationally. It researches, develops, produces, and sells solar photovoltaic glass, and solar cell modules and related products; and processes, produces, and supplies quartz sand. The company is also involved in the construction and operation of solar power stations in Nanjing, Liquan, and Hefei; and manufactures and markets lithium battery anode materials, electronic silver paste, and related materials of flat panel display. In addition, it engages in the trading of solar modules and other related accessories. Further, IRICO Group New Energy Company Limited invests in properties; develops and produces flat shadow products; and manufactures electronic devices and components, as well as engages in mining exploration activities. The company was formerly known as IRICO Group Electronics Company Limited and changed its name to IRICO Group New Energy Company Limited in January 2016. The company was founded in 2004 and is based in Xianyang, the People’s Republic of China. IRICO Group New Energy Company Limited is a subsidiary of IRICO Group Corporation.
  			

