 Career History



President & Executive Director

                                    1981 - Current                


IRICO Group New Energy Co. Ltd.


                  IRICO Group New Energy Co. Ltd. manufactures photovoltaic glass, liquid display glass substrate and display devices. It involves in the manufacturing and trading of color picture tubes, luminous materials, liquid crystal related products, thin film liquid display glass substrate and display devices, and solar photovoltaic glass. The company was founded on September 10, 2004 and is headquartered in Xianyang, China.                




General Manager

                                    2001 - 2003                


Shenzhen Hongyang Industry & Trade Co., Ltd.


                  Shenzhen Hongyang Industry & Trade Co., Ltd., a subsidiary of Government of China, is a Chinese company located in Shenzhen. The firm engages in import and export services.                





